This is the README file for the extrelation package.
Author: Fabian Pijcke
E-mail: fabian@pijcke.net
Comments and suggestions are welcome.
Date: March 2017
Version: 0.1

Extrelation supports research in the field of relational databases by providing
simple commands and environments to produce relations given by extension.

Features include customization of elements composing the relation, vertical and
horizontal partitioning, and some stylistic modifiers.

The files in this distribution are:

extrelation.sty     - implementation
extrelation.tex     - documentation sources
extrelation.pdf     - documentation

Licensing of this package is covered by LPPL.
